{"tid":1646530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十八區 全力文宣 勇武如水","createTime":"2019-10-11T10:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T04:16:56.000Z","uid":69845,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"89aa5937c0683ef1ef27518108633a0f43f20863","tid":1646530,"uid":69845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:36:37.000Z","msg":"之前開咗個11/10 全民文宣 推唔起<br />\n<br />\n今次 如同意 幫手推推<br />\n<br />\n第一<br />\n呢一兩個星期有好多事 請一齊做文宣又好 唱國歌又好 <br />\n助燃革命之火<br />\n<br />\nTg 文宣group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=21020bee\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a><br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n十八區 勇武如水<br />\n勇武 除左提醒大家 我地係抗爭緊 仲有對付中資 追究性侵<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請Be Water</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">手足係最重要 希望唔需要去到打狗 救人嘅地步</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hDWAzdu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhDWAzdu.jpg&h=cc7ff15b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOdGuMQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOdGuMQ.jpg&h=377750f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXURR0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXURR0b.jpg&h=f4437a6f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QSvNqkc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQSvNqkc.jpg&h=8d6a85f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zu7TkTy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZu7TkTy.jpg&h=1a297e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/11/183603_aceea3a21dc5eb8cb36aae7995223869.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F11%2F183603_aceea3a21dc5eb8cb36aae7995223869.png&h=ba273070&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01b496dabcd7480d5c6d5e705e51cfceef554d24","tid":1646530,"uid":69845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:42:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17855e29eb1c4f6bc9395e916ea9d0fe75140c5f","tid":1646530,"uid":69845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32075b01c9b2ec1354400be2c69e8d8c0d003f06","tid":1646530,"uid":69845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:42:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9ef0289c0ed7da3826c2744bd7b02ae7879d793","tid":1646530,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:43:41.000Z","msg":"☺"},{"pid":"955039381c30a8d735d6ed6d478607dfb9ba5eb5","tid":1646530,"uid":270374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保護前線 刻不容緩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人，我哋眾籌咗好多次，賣廣告、出書、拍電影&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n但係最重要嘅，係買裝備保護前線!!!!<br />\n而唔係等佢哋受傷咗之後先去支援佢地!!!<br />\n<br />\n請大家快啲支持YHF！過咗一日，先得十幾人支持，好傷心<br />\n係，我無Fact check，但係我情願相信，呢個世界有人願意冒被捕風險，都要做眾籌<br />\n希望大家衡量過後，可以支持做實事嘅團隊。<br />\n件事未完，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輸贏都好，保護手足應該係和理非最需要關心嘅事。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1643523/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1643523/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/payments/?oid=1662043&amp;err=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fpayments%2F%3Foid%3D1662043%26err%3D1&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=9c25418a\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/payments/?oid=1662043&amp;err=1</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TJhHcCt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTJhHcCt.jpg&h=5bcbfa54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68e48266ea73df523a34c14e5cbc7d6a35464432","tid":1646530,"uid":69845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T11:04:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6f26125529ac0c32e7e47e98084c97633fb9790","tid":1646530,"uid":9258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:12:19.000Z","msg":"推，唔好俾五毛分左去講生日慶祝"},{"pid":"9d72bc41d52e36af1ebc2d685f0a92582b8e2653","tid":1646530,"uid":119597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11b6e455737b65cffd31c56ae77c5c937dfd99b","tid":1646530,"uid":80139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:12:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3aa0d4ab1f7a4501acd7e56de48dd27eed27d91","tid":1646530,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:13:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ecc0182d54e312faa64a307fa7741890bdbf3ac","tid":1646530,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:14:44.000Z","msg":"Wow"},{"pid":"fea44d2ae18a7699bc280518698d8a1a2a203022","tid":1646530,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:15:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da13a731c86d520975ea0195753ee774fa8435c7","tid":1646530,"uid":80139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:15:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"555f4e15a34beeb58209a572fa1f7dbec68dfc0d","tid":1646530,"uid":69845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:16:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"897b4159c7d6858c7aa1baf7f4176ff50f13fc9d","tid":1646530,"uid":247798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:17:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6890e4aa0120735c227358ebc9c4efc264918346","tid":1646530,"uid":80139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:17:55.000Z","msg